data.description: Are you looking for tons of privacy on a large lot surrounded by woods, then look no further!  Almost 1700 square feet on one level. Come see this beautifully updated kitchen with all new custom cabinets with coffee bar, quartz counter tops, and backsplash. Relax in the cozy living room with wood beams and gas fireplace with programmable remote. There is an additional sunken den as well. Mohawk LVP flooring throughout most of home.  Master bedroom is tucked away for added privacy. There are even 2 water heaters with the master bath having its own to enjoy without worry. Large laundry room with cabinets for storage and its own separate entrance. There is an enclosed back porch that can be opened to screen in summer to enjoy year round. Seller also added a patio area for more entertaining space. 2 additional storage buildings in back remain. There is extensive landscaping and flowers around the home for extra curb appeal. Owner has covered with leaves to protect for winter. Very large back yard for plenty of parking or whatever your imagination holds. Roof is only 6 years old. Make your appointment today!
